setFolder

public void setFolder(java.lang.String folder)
Sets the folder where the measurement should be saved. Be aware that an additional folder is created inside this folder when the measurement starts, which indicates the specific time when the measurement was started. This is done since one measurement can be started multiple times. To obtain the full path to this subfolder, use the respective function in MeasurementSaver.

Parameters:
folder - the folder of the measurement.
